  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="docs-content" id="docsContent">
    <div class="docs-header">
      <div class="docs-breadcrumb">
        <a href="index.html">Home</a><span>›</span>
        <span>Dokumentasi</span><span>›</span>
        <span>Getting Started</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="docs-title">DOKUMENTASI</h1>
      <p class="docs-subtitle">
        Panduan lengkap untuk memaksimalkan YURI MUSIC di server Discord Anda. Dari setup dasar hingga semua music commands, semuanya ada di sini.
      </p>
      <div class="docs-meta">
        <span class="meta-badge">📚 Lengkap & Detail</span>
        <span class="meta-badge">🔄 Selalu Update</span>
        <span class="meta-badge">🎵 25+ Music Commands</span>
        <span class="meta-badge">🌟 Mudah Dipahami</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Links -->
    <div class="content-section">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span class="section-icon">🚀</span>Quick Start Guide</h2>
      <div class="quick-links">
        <a href="#setup" class="quick-link-card">
          <div class="quick-link-icon">⚙️</div>
          <div class="quick-link-title">Setup Bot</div>
          <p class="quick-link-desc">Undang dan atur YURI MUSIC di server Anda</p>
        </a>
        <a href="#play-cmd" class="quick-link-card">
          <div class="quick-link-icon">🎵</div>
          <div class="quick-link-title">Music Commands</div>
          <p class="quick-link-desc">25+ commands musik lengkap dari file server</p>
        </a>
        <a href="#features" class="quick-link-card">
          <div class="quick-link-icon">✨</div>
          <div class="quick-link-title">Features</div>
          <p class="quick-link-desc">Eksplorasi semua fitur YURI MUSIC</p>
        </a>
        <a href="#troubleshooting" class="quick-link-card">
          <div class="quick-link-icon">🔧</div>
          <div class="quick-link-title">Troubleshooting</div>
          <p class="quick-link-desc">Solusi untuk masalah umum</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Introduction -->
    <div class="content-section" id="intro">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span class="section-icon">📖</span>Introduction</h2>
      <p class="section-text">
        <strong>YURI MUSIC</strong> adalah Discord bot all-in-one yang dirancang untuk membuat server Discord Anda lebih hidup. Dengan 25+ music commands yang powerful, leveling system, economy, dan moderation tools, YURI MUSIC adalah solusi sempurna untuk server dari berbagai ukuran.
      </p>
      <p class="section-text">
        Bot ini dilengkapi <strong>music system 24/7</strong>, <strong>filter & equalizer</strong>, <strong>playlist support</strong>, <strong>seek & skipto</strong>, dan masih banyak lagi. Semua command menggunakan Discord Slash Commands untuk kemudahan penggunaan.
      </p>
      <div class="info-box tip">
        <div class="info-icon">💡</div>
        <div class="info-content">
          <div class="info-title">Pro Tip</div>
          <p class="info-text">Mulai dengan <code>/help</code> untuk melihat semua fitur dan <code>/setup</code> untuk konfigurasi awal yang cepat!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Setup Guide -->
    <div class="content-section" id="setup">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span class="section-icon">⚙️</span>Setup Guide</h2>
      <p class="section-text">Ikuti langkah berikut untuk mengatur YURI MUSIC di server Discord Anda:</p>
      <ol class="steps-list">
        <li class="step-item">
          <div class="step-number"></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3 class="step-title">Undang Bot ke Server</h3>
            <p class="step-desc">Klik "Invite Bot" di halaman utama. Pastikan Anda memiliki permission "Manage Server". Pilih server dan klik "Authorize".</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="step-item">
          <div class="step-number"></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3 class="step-title">Atur Permissions</h3>
            <p class="step-desc">YURI MUSIC memerlukan: <strong>Send Messages</strong>, <strong>Embed Links</strong>, <strong>Connect</strong>, <strong>Speak</strong>, dan <strong>Manage Roles</strong> untuk fitur auto-role.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="step-item">
          <div class="step-number"></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3 class="step-title">Jalankan Setup Wizard</h3>
            <p class="step-desc">Gunakan <code>/setup</code> untuk menjalankan setup wizard interaktif — konfigurasi music channels, leveling, welcome messages, dll dengan mudah.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="step-item">
          <div class="step-number"></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3 class="step-title">Kustomisasi Settings</h3>
            <p class="step-desc">Gunakan <code>/config</code> untuk panel konfigurasi lengkap. Atur prefix custom, aktifkan/nonaktifkan fitur, sesuaikan bot sesuai kebutuhan server.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="step-item">
          <div class="step-number"></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3 class="step-title">Siap!</h3>
            <p class="step-desc">Bot sudah siap! Coba <code>/play [nama lagu]</code> untuk langsung memutar musik.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <div class="info-box warning">
        <div class="info-icon">⚠️</div>
        <div class="info-content">
          <div class="info-title">Penting!</div>
          <p class="info-text">Pastikan role bot berada di atas role yang ingin di-manage agar fitur auto-role dan moderation berfungsi dengan baik.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══ MUSIC COMMANDS - FROM SCREENSHOTS ═══ -->
    <div class="content-section" id="play-cmd">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span class="section-icon">🎵</span>Music Commands</h2>
      <p class="section-text">
        Semua command musik YURI MUSIC — diambil langsung dari file server. Total <strong>25 commands</strong> tersedia.
      </p>

      <div class="tabs">
        <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab(event, 'tab-all')">Semua</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab(event, 'tab-playback')">▶ Playback</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab(event, 'tab-queue')">📋 Queue</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab(event, 'tab-control')">🎛️ Control</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab(event, 'tab-extra')">⚙️ Extra</button>
      </div>

      <!-- ALL -->
      <div class="tab-panel active" id="tab-all">
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">▶️ /play <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Putar musik dari YouTube, Spotify, atau SoundCloud. Mendukung URL langsung dan pencarian nama lagu.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /play &lt;nama lagu atau URL&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏸️ /pause <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Pause musik yang sedang diputar. Gunakan /resume untuk melanjutkan.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /pause</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">▶️ /resume <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Lanjutkan musik yang sedang di-pause.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /resume</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏭️ /skip <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Skip lagu yang sedang diputar dan lanjut ke lagu berikutnya di queue.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /skip</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏭️ /skipto <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Skip langsung ke posisi tertentu di queue. Lagu sebelumnya akan dihapus dari queue.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /skipto &lt;nomor posisi&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏹️ /stop <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Stop musik dan hapus semua queue. Bot akan tetap berada di voice channel.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /stop</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">📋 /queue <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Tampilkan daftar lagu yang ada di queue saat ini beserta durasi total.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /queue [halaman]</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">❌ /remove <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Hapus lagu tertentu dari queue berdasarkan nomor posisi.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /remove &lt;nomor posisi&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔀 /shuffle <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Acak urutan lagu yang ada di queue secara random.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /shuffle</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔁 /loop <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Toggle loop untuk lagu yang sedang diputar. Lagu akan diulang terus menerus.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /loop</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔁 /loopqueue <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Toggle loop untuk seluruh queue. Setelah semua lagu diputar, akan kembali dari awal.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /loopqueue</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">📻 /nowplaying <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Tampilkan informasi detail lagu yang sedang diputar beserta progress bar.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /nowplaying</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔊 /volume <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Atur volume musik antara 0 hingga 100. Default volume adalah 100.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /volume &lt;0-100&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔍 /search <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Cari lagu dan pilih dari beberapa hasil pencarian sebelum diputar.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /search &lt;kata kunci&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏩ /seek <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Lompat ke timestamp tertentu dalam lagu yang sedang diputar.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /seek &lt;detik&gt; atau &lt;mm:ss&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔄 /replay <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Putar ulang lagu dari awal tanpa harus mencari lagu lagi.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /replay</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">📁 /playlist <span class="command-badge badge-premium">PREMIUM</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Kelola playlist pribadi. Simpan, load, dan share playlist dengan mudah.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /playlist &lt;save|load|delete|list&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🎚️ /filter <span class="command-badge badge-premium">PREMIUM</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Terapkan audio filter seperti bassboost, nightcore, vaporwave, 8d, dan lainnya.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /filter &lt;nama filter&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔀 /move <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Pindahkan lagu dari satu posisi ke posisi lain dalam queue.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /move &lt;dari&gt; &lt;ke&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🗑️ /clear <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Hapus semua lagu dari queue. Lagu yang sedang diputar tidak akan terpengaruh.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /clear</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔌 /join <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Paksa bot masuk ke voice channel Anda tanpa memutar musik.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /join</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">👋 /leave <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Keluarkan bot dari voice channel dan hentikan semua musik.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /leave</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🕐 /autoplay <span class="command-badge badge-premium">PREMIUM</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Aktifkan autoplay — bot otomatis memainkan lagu baru saat queue habis berdasarkan rekomendasi.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /autoplay</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏰ /247 <span class="command-badge badge-premium">PREMIUM</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Aktifkan mode 24/7 — bot tetap di voice channel meskipun queue kosong dan tidak ada yang mendengarkan.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /247</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">❓ /help <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Tampilkan daftar semua command yang tersedia dengan deskripsi singkat.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /help [command]</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PLAYBACK -->
      <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-playback">
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">▶️ /play <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Putar musik dari YouTube, Spotify, atau SoundCloud.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /play &lt;nama lagu atau URL&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏸️ /pause <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Pause musik yang sedang diputar.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /pause</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">▶️ /resume <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Lanjutkan musik yang sedang di-pause.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /resume</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏹️ /stop <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Stop musik dan hapus semua queue.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /stop</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔄 /replay <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Putar ulang lagu dari awal.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /replay</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔍 /search <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Cari lagu dan pilih dari hasil pencarian.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /search &lt;kata kunci&gt;</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- QUEUE -->
      <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-queue">
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">📋 /queue <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Tampilkan daftar lagu di queue saat ini.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /queue [halaman]</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">❌ /remove <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Hapus lagu dari queue berdasarkan posisi.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /remove &lt;nomor posisi&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🗑️ /clear <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Hapus semua lagu dari queue.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /clear</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔀 /shuffle <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Acak urutan lagu di queue.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /shuffle</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔀 /move <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Pindahkan lagu dalam queue.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /move &lt;dari&gt; &lt;ke&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏭️ /skipto <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Skip ke posisi tertentu di queue.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /skipto &lt;nomor posisi&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">📁 /playlist <span class="command-badge badge-premium">PREMIUM</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Kelola playlist pribadi.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /playlist &lt;save|load|delete|list&gt;</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CONTROL -->
      <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-control">
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔊 /volume <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Atur volume musik (0–100).</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /volume &lt;0-100&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏩ /seek <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Lompat ke timestamp tertentu dalam lagu.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /seek &lt;detik&gt; atau &lt;mm:ss&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔁 /loop <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Toggle loop lagu saat ini.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /loop</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔁 /loopqueue <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Toggle loop seluruh queue.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /loopqueue</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">📻 /nowplaying <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Info lagu yang sedang diputar + progress bar.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /nowplaying</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏭️ /skip <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Skip ke lagu berikutnya.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /skip</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- EXTRA -->
      <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-extra">
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🎚️ /filter <span class="command-badge badge-premium">PREMIUM</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Terapkan audio filter (bassboost, nightcore, 8d, vaporwave, dll).</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /filter &lt;nama filter&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🕐 /autoplay <span class="command-badge badge-premium">PREMIUM</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Autoplay lagu baru saat queue habis.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /autoplay</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">⏰ /247 <span class="command-badge badge-premium">PREMIUM</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Mode 24/7 — bot tidak keluar dari voice channel.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /247</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">🔌 /join <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Bot masuk ke voice channel Anda.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /join</div>
        </div>
        <div class="command-card">
          <div class="command-name">👋 /leave <span class="command-badge badge-free">FREE</span></div>
          <div class="command-desc">Bot keluar dari voice channel.</div>
          <div class="command-usage">Usage: /leave</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Code Examples -->
    <div class="content-section" id="quickstart">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span class="section-icon">💻</span>Contoh Penggunaan</h2>
      <div class="code-block">
        <div class="code-header">
          <span class="code-lang">Discord Slash Commands</span>
          <button class="code-copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
        </div>
        <pre class="code-content"><span class="comment">// Putar lagu dari YouTube</span>
<span class="keyword">/play</span> <span class="string">Bohemian Rhapsody</span>

<span class="comment">// Putar dari Spotify URL</span>
<span class="keyword">/play</span> <span class="string">https://open.spotify.com/track/...</span>

<span class="comment">// Skip ke posisi 5 dalam queue</span>
<span class="keyword">/skipto</span> <span class="string">5</span>

<span class="comment">// Seek ke menit 2:30</span>
<span class="keyword">/seek</span> <span class="string">2:30</span>

<span class="comment">// Aktifkan filter bassboost</span>
<span class="keyword">/filter</span> <span class="string">bassboost</span>

<span class="comment">// Pindah lagu dari posisi 3 ke posisi 1</span>
<span class="keyword">/move</span> <span class="string">3 1</span>

<span class="comment">// Aktifkan 24/7 mode (Premium)</span>
<span class="keyword">/247</span></pre>
      </div>
      <div class="info-box info">
        <div class="info-icon">ℹ️</div>
        <div class="info-content">
          <div class="info-title">Slash Commands</div>
          <p class="info-text">Ketik <code>/</code> di chat Discord untuk melihat semua command dengan auto-complete! Command Premium ditandai dengan badge kuning 🟡.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Overview -->
    <div class="content-section" id="features">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span class="section-icon">✨</span>Features Overview</h2>
      <h3 style="color:#a78bfa;font-size:1.5rem;margin:25px 0 15px;">🎵 Music System</h3>
      <p class="section-text">Support <strong>YouTube, Spotify, SoundCloud</strong>. Queue management, loop, shuffle, seek, skipto, move. Audio filters termasuk bassboost, nightcore, 8d audio, vaporwave. Mode 24/7 dan autoplay tersedia untuk Premium.</p>

      <h3 id="leveling" style="color:#a78bfa;font-size:1.5rem;margin:25px 0 15px;">⭐ Leveling System</h3>
      <p class="section-text">XP otomatis dari chat dan voice activity. <strong>Animated rank card</strong> yang dikustomisasi, global leaderboard, auto-role rewards saat level up.</p>

      <h3 id="economy" style="color:#a78bfa;font-size:1.5rem;margin:25px 0 15px;">💰 Economy System</h3>
      <p class="section-text">Virtual currency lengkap dengan bank system, daily/weekly rewards, work commands, shop items, gambling games (slots, coinflip, blackjack), dan transfer antar users.</p>

      <h3 id="moderation" style="color:#a78bfa;font-size:1.5rem;margin:25px 0 15px;">🛡️ Moderation Tools</h3>
      <p class="section-text"><strong>Auto-moderation</strong> (anti-spam, anti-link, bad words filter), ban/kick/mute, warning system, raid protection, dan detail logging untuk semua aksi moderasi.</p>

      <div class="info-box tip">
        <div class="info-icon">🚀</div>
        <div class="info-content">
          <div class="info-title">Coming Soon</div>
          <p class="info-text">Kami terus menambahkan fitur baru! Follow Discord server kami untuk update terbaru.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Troubleshooting -->
    <div class="content-section" id="troubleshooting">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span class="section-icon">🔧</span>Troubleshooting</h2>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">🔇 Bot tidak memutar musik</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Pastikan bot sudah join voice channel kamu terlebih dahulu dengan <code>/join</code>. Cek permission bot: <strong>Connect</strong> dan <strong>Speak</strong> harus aktif. Coba <code>/leave</code> lalu <code>/play</code> ulang.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">📋 Queue tidak muncul</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Pastikan ada lagu di queue. Coba gunakan <code>/nowplaying</code> untuk cek status. Jika kosong, tambahkan lagu dengan <code>/play</code>.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">🎚️ Filter tidak berfungsi</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Filter memerlukan Premium. Upgrade ke Premium untuk akses semua filter audio termasuk bassboost, nightcore, dan 8d audio.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">⚡ Bot lag atau disconnect</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Bot mungkin sedang overload. Coba <code>/leave</code> dan <code>/join</code> ulang. Jika masalah berlanjut, hubungi support server kami.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="content-section" id="faq">
      <h2 class="section-title"><span class="section-icon">❓</span>FAQ</h2>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Apakah YURI MUSIC gratis?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Ya, YURI MUSIC 100% gratis untuk fitur dasar (20 commands)! Premium menambahkan fitur seperti filter, autoplay, playlist, dan mode 24/7.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Platform musik apa yang didukung?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">YURI MUSIC mendukung <strong>YouTube</strong>, <strong>Spotify</strong>, dan <strong>SoundCloud</strong>. Anda bisa menggunakan URL langsung atau mencari dengan nama lagu.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Bagaimana cara mendapatkan support?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Join Discord support server kami atau buat ticket dengan command <code>/ticket</code>. Tim support siap membantu 24/7!</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Apakah data saya aman?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Sangat aman! Kami menggunakan enkripsi untuk semua data sensitif. Baca <a href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a> kami untuk detail lengkap.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>
</div>

